*smplayer-0.7.0 (01 Feb 2012)

  01 Feb 2012; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org> +smplayer-0.7.0.ebuild,
  smplayer-9999.ebuild:
  Version bump to 0.7.0. This version fixes bug #345653. Drop quit.patch, now
  applied upstream. Add mplayer[X], bug #377343. Sync live ebuild with release
  version ebuild.

  10 Jan 2012; Nikos Chantziaras <realnc@gmail.com> smplayer-9999.ebuild:
  Build against system quazip

  01 Dec 2011; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> smplayer-9999.ebuild:
  update mplayer2 dep

  16 Sep 2011; Steve Dibb <beandog@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Remove smplayer-0.6.9-r1.ebuild, moved to portage tree

  06 Aug 2011; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> smplayer-0.6.9-r1.ebuild,
  smplayer-9999.ebuild:
  mplayer2 renamed USE ass to libass

  16 Mar 2011; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> smplayer-0.6.9-r1.ebuild,
  smplayer-9999.ebuild:
  mplayer-uau -> mplayer2 rename

*smplayer-0.6.9-r1 (10 Jun 2010)

